name: Villainy Studios
body:
### Welcome to Villainy Studios
We're a small team of developers who code because we can.  More projects and developers will likely find their way here before long.

Currently we're a two-man team consisting of:
  + Joseph Preston (@jpreston86) 
  + Joshua Embrey (@MrSchism)


## Status
This page is currently using the Static Site Generator and a stock theme.  That won't last.

If you want to contact us, email @MrSchism at `mrschism[@]sdf[.]org`
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
